                            <div class="text-justify">
                                Software Engineer<br><br>
                                <div class="ml-5">
                                    <ul class='list-disc'>
                                        <li>Perform daily system maintenance and transactional upkeep</li>
                                        <li>Work along an international team to develop an application for Unit Trust funds</li>
                                        <li>Work along multiple companies to cater for the need of the applications, FPX for payment processing and TNG for application hosting</li>
                                        <li>Analyse business and legal requirement, ensuring applications follows the required security requirements, and business logic required</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                
