                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-start md:text-end mb-10">
                            <time class="font-mono italic">Nov. 2022 - Feb. 2023</time>
                            <div class="text-lg font-black">WonderPod Sdn. Bhd.</div>
                            <div class=""> System Research (Trainee)</div> <br>
                            <div class="text-justify">
                            Manage and enhance front-end aspects of WordPress websites, emphasizing vigilant monitoring on Amazon Web Services, tasks such as renewing security certificates and prompt restarts during downtime.
