                        <div class="timeline-start md:text-end mb-10">
                            <time class="font-mono italic">Feb. 2021 - Nov. 2022</time>
                            <div class="text-lg font-black">Seizure Prediction and Prevention</div>
                            <div>Two ReactJS applications, 1 Firebase server</div><br>
                            <div class="text-justify">
                                Lead collaborative efforts in designing and developing a front-end application aimed at aiding doctors in monitoring patient signs. Develop a ReactJS-based dashboard for doctors, proficiently retrieving data from a centralized Firebase server through webhooks and RESTful APIs. Additionally, design, maintain, and enhance a mobile application serving as a data collection tool for patients, leveraging ReactJS and RESTful APIs for optimal functionality.
