                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-end mb-10">
                            <time class="font-mono italic">August. 2022 - Nov. 2022</time>
                            <div class="text-lg font-black">Secure Coding for Software Developers</div>
                            <div class="text-justify">
                                Final Year Projects<br><br>
                                Conduct in-depth investigations into the influence of diversity and corporate training initiatives on programmers' adherence to secure coding guidelines. Methodically gather and analyze data to ascertain effective training methodologies that promote programmers' compliance with stringent security guidelines. Leverage insights to contribute to the development of comprehensive strategies for fostering a secure coding environment within diverse and dynamic corporate settings.
